                </p>

                <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className="flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label className={labelClass} style={{ color: "var(--text-muted)" }}>
                            Project Title <span style={{ color: "#f87171" }}>*</span>
